1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 20=

3
00:00:12,160 --> 00:00:13,800
Dear guests,

4
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:16,390
on the journey of love,

5
00:00:17,070 --> 00:00:19,280
(Bride)
a ring is more than a token.

6
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:20,670
It is a promise.

7
00:00:21,190 --> 00:00:24,960
It is eternal proof
that two destined hearts are joined.

8
00:00:27,350 --> 00:00:31,390
Now, please stand face to face.

9
00:00:31,960 --> 00:00:34,920
Look deeply into each other's eyes.

10
00:00:36,750 --> 00:00:42,150
Now, let us witness
their promise of love.

11
00:00:42,150 --> 00:00:44,840
- Yes!
- Yes!

12
00:00:52,470 --> 00:00:53,280
Wait!

13
00:01:02,220 --> 00:01:02,980
Hey!

14
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:04,040
The ring's dirty.

15
00:01:05,349 --> 00:01:06,560
I'll clean it for you.

16
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:08,150
Alright, next,

17
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:10,430
please put the rings

18
00:01:10,430 --> 00:01:12,480
on each other's left ring finger.

19
00:01:12,510 --> 00:01:14,200
Jiang Zechen, are you insane?

20
00:01:16,430 --> 00:01:19,400
(I'm the groom, and you're
putting the ring on the bride?)

21
00:01:27,430 --> 00:01:28,280
Don't worry.

22
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,680
I'm not here to ruin your wedding.

23
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:32,310
(Yeah, right.)

24
00:01:34,150 --> 00:01:34,950
I wish you...

25
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,310
I wish you both happiness.

26
00:01:41,870 --> 00:01:43,590
Isn't that Jiang Zechen?

27
00:01:44,150 --> 00:01:44,950
Yeah.

28
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:46,710
Why's he the best man?

29
00:01:46,710 --> 00:01:49,310
The ex-husband
became the best man? Interesting.

30
00:01:51,230 --> 00:01:54,120
Qiao Nian, there's something
I've always wanted to tell you.

31
00:01:57,350 --> 00:01:58,870
Since the day I met you,

32
00:01:59,430 --> 00:02:00,760
I've liked you.

33
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,920
I still do.

34
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:04,480
Song Che,

35
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:08,910
I really can't promise you
anything beyond our deal.

36
00:02:10,870 --> 00:02:13,190
Is it because of Jiang Zechen?

37
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:26,520
Don't risk yourself for me again.

38
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:29,870
That creep isn't worth it.

39
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:31,120
It's worth it to me.

40
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:36,080
Qiao Nian, Jiang Zechen
got hurt playing basketball.

41
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,280
Aren't you going to check on him?

42
00:02:38,470 --> 00:02:40,030
Please look after him for me.

43
00:02:41,310 --> 00:02:42,750
Hey, Qiao Nian!

44
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,840
(My place in Qiao Nian's heart)

45
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:48,150
(still can't compare to Jiang Zechen.)

46
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:49,960
Song Che,

47
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:54,000
to me, you're a friend I can trust.

48
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:59,000
You're also a very reliable partner.

49
00:03:04,670 --> 00:03:06,710
You're completely useless.

50
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:09,470
I never should've trusted you.

51
00:03:11,310 --> 00:03:12,680
In the end,

52
00:03:14,470 --> 00:03:18,150
you still couldn't bear
to hurt Qiao Nian, could you?

53
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:28,560
Of course. After more
than ten years of feelings,

54
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:31,800
how could that be so easy to destroy?

55
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:43,630
Kneel.

56
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:48,710
I said kneel!

57
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:50,800
(For Qiao Nian,)

58
00:03:51,830 --> 00:03:53,510
(I'll endure it.)

59
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,710
What's wrong? Are you feeling sick?

60
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:06,240
(Zechen...)

61
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,800
Go rest in the dressing room.

62
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:31,120
Come on. I'll take you to get changed.

63
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:31,720
Okay.

64
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:53,310
I'll leave the second half
of the act to you.

65
00:04:53,630 --> 00:04:55,920
Don't worry. This is what I do best.

66
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:57,000
Go on.

67
00:04:57,430 --> 00:04:58,070
Thanks.

68
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:03,120
Be careful.

69
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,160
Let's go.

70
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,240
(She's so beautiful.)

71
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:18,560
Why are you staring?

72
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:19,560
Oh.

73
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,040
It's nothing.

74
00:05:22,270 --> 00:05:24,040
What? Qiao Nian left,

75
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,950
and your soul left too?

76
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:29,360
For a second, I almost thought
this wedding was real.

77
00:05:30,430 --> 00:05:32,120
Then I'll finish
the second half with you.

78
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:34,120
Wow, you're really getting into it.

79
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:37,680
Let me show you
what real acting looks like.

80
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:39,680
There's no way I won't clear this level.

81
00:05:50,900 --> 00:05:51,700
Congrats.

82
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:52,750
Whoa.

83
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:54,390
You're gorgeous.

84
00:05:54,390 --> 00:05:55,190
Thank you.

85
00:05:55,870 --> 00:05:57,070
You guys acted really well.

86
00:05:57,070 --> 00:05:57,630
We'll double your pay.

87
00:05:57,630 --> 00:05:59,120
Hey, thank you, boss.

88
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,630
Miss, this is for you.

89
00:06:02,650 --> 00:06:03,930
It's the key to the secret room.

90
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:04,950
Okay.

91
00:06:14,180 --> 00:06:16,060
(Is Mom really locked inside?)

92
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:42,750
(Mom has been drawing
my favorite dolphins.)

93
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:52,870
Mom.

94
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:08,960
Mom!

95
00:07:11,430 --> 00:07:12,240
Nian!

96
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,720
Mom!

97
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:20,310
Mom!

98
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:22,040
Let me look at you.

99
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:23,430
Mom!

100
00:07:23,830 --> 00:07:25,360
Nian...

101
00:07:29,190 --> 00:07:32,240
Mom, why do you look so worn out?

102
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,920
Mom!

103
00:07:42,870 --> 00:07:43,680
Mom,

104
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:45,090
we don't have much time.

105
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,270
I'll get you out first.

106
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:50,600
- Okay, let's go.
- Let's go.

107
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:58,750
I told you to ruin the wedding.

108
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:02,160
Instead, to distract me,

109
00:08:02,310 --> 00:08:03,870
you switched out the bride!

110
00:08:04,190 --> 00:08:05,190
Where did Qiao Nian go?

111
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:07,390
Where is Qiao Nian? Where is she?

112
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:09,070
Mr. Jiang, bad news.

113
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,480
What happened?

114
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,750
The secret room door was opened.

115
00:08:12,070 --> 00:08:13,310
Ms. Xie is gone too.

116
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,360
What?

117
00:08:19,330 --> 00:08:25,300
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

118
00:08:25,580 --> 00:08:33,180
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

119
00:08:33,230 --> 00:08:37,020
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

120
00:08:37,540 --> 00:08:40,820
♪Where this ends♪

121
00:08:40,820 --> 00:08:48,100
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

122
00:08:48,100 --> 00:08:52,430
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

123
00:08:52,470 --> 00:08:55,550
♪Love turns into pain♪

124
00:08:55,620 --> 00:08:59,740
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

125
00:08:59,900 --> 00:09:03,380
♪Yet I still want you close♪

126
00:09:03,380 --> 00:09:07,550
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

127
00:09:07,550 --> 00:09:10,860
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

128
00:09:10,860 --> 00:09:15,430
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

129
00:09:15,430 --> 00:09:21,740
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

130
